description: Recently sold: $174,900. Amazing year-round cabin on sought after Prairie Lake! This neat and charming cabin offers an entry foyer which opens to the kitchen, dining and living room. The lower level has been completely updated and offers a large walk-in shower room, private 1/2 bath, and a large room for additional sleeping, storage, and utilities. Comes complete with fmost furniture, and TV and many items that would make this place ready to use right away! Outside you have a 12 x 24 deck lakeside, a 16 x 24 garage with overhead doors on the road side and lake side, a finished bunkhouse for guests, fire ring, and additional bdlg for storage. description: Recently sold: $195,000. Live the full Minnesota experience in this spacious home on Tamarack Lake. This summer, relax on the deck, feel the sand under your toes on the 150 feet of shoreline, or take your boat out for a cruise. The lake offers Bluegill, Crappie, Northern Pike, and Perch, if you like to fish.   Come home to a spacious, open floor plan- perfect for entertaining. On the main level- the living room, with large windows overlooking the lake; a dining room; and the spacious kitchen with bright, plentiful cabinets; as well as two bedrooms and a full bath. Downstairs hosts two more bedrooms; a bath with a whirlpool tub; an extra room for a den, office or hobby space; a family room; bar area with a walk-out to the yard; and laundry room.  In the winter, enjoy snowmobiling on the nearby trails, which connect to a network of trails that criss-cross the state. Hunters will enjoy the nearby Memorial WMA land. After a day of fun, come home and relax by the fire. Don't miss this one!
